# [[to tell the truth]], [[to be honest|to be completely honest]], [[to be frank|to be completely frank]]
#: {{syn|fr|à vrai dire|à dire la vérité|pour être honnête|pour être franc}}

====Usage notes====
* Can also be used with an indirect object: ''pour tout te dire'', ''pour tout vous dire'' ("to be completely honest with you").
